A cohort study on anticoagulant therapy risks in dental patients after multiple 
extractions.

Matarese M(1)(2), Cervino G(1), Fiorillo L(3)(4), Stelitano C(1), Imbesi 
Bellantoni M(1), Meto A(5), Greco Lucchina A(6), Tornello FA(7), Runci Anastasi 
