Protocol for the models of primary osteoporosis screening in men (MOPS) cluster 
randomized trial.

Colón-Emeric CS(1), Lee R(2), Pieper CF(3), Lyles KW(2), Zullig LL(2), Nelson 
RE(4), Robinson K(5), Igwe I(5), Jadhav J(5), Adler RA(6).

