Pancreaticoduodenectomy in octogenarians: The importance of "biological age" on 
clinical outcomes.

Quero G(1), Pecorelli N(2), Paiella S(3), Fiorillo C(4), Petrone MC(2), Capretti 
G(5), Laterza V(6), De Sio D(6), Menghi R(6), Kauffmann E(7), Nobile S(3), 
